.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE_CHANNEL_OPENS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-channel-opens \- list channels by state, optionally pending only
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-channel-opens

.SH DESCRIPTION
Lists peer channels. With --pending, filters to non-NORMAL non-CLOSED states.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
